 configure_frame_options # Configure the application options for frame creation
   -mode (block_and_trim|preserve_and_convert|preserve_all|keep_obs_and_trim_touch_pin|keep_obs_and_trim_all_pin)
                          (The frame configuration mode: 
                           Values: block_and_trim, preserve_and_convert, 
                           preserve_all, keep_obs_and_trim_touch_pin, 
                           keep_obs_and_trim_all_pin)
   [-block designName]    (The design name)
   [-script_only]         (Only output the application options to the console)
   [lib_cell_list]        (List of lib cells to configure frame options)

